    <!-- Changelog page -->
    <string name="changelog_title">Changelog</string>
    <string-array name="changelog_0_12">
        <item>Added premium feature: moon &amp; tide.</item>
        <item>Adjusted page layout.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="changelog_0_11">
        <item>UI improvements.</item>
        <item>About page UI improvements.</item>
        <item>AR eye safety: calibration only within 45 min of sunset; camera auto-pauses as it nears the sun while keeping the sunset overlay.</item>
        <item>Improved bridge rendering.</item>
    </string-array>
    <string-array name="changelog_0_10">
        <item>Map: new playback controls on the date row. “&lt;”/“&gt;” step one day back/forward; “&lt;&lt;”/“&gt;&gt;” play continuously — each tap cycles the speed (0.5s → 0.1s → 0.05s → stop), shown by the number of arrows.</item>
        <item>Focal simulator: the time axis now starts at 12:00 with a dynamic end of sunset + 10 minutes.</item>
        <item>Focal simulator: three-tier non-linear time scale, finer the closer to sunset (fine within 90 min before sunset, ultra-fine within 10 min), with the sunset point marked on the axis.</item>
        <item>Hotspot fixes.</item>
        <item>Added English language support, switchable on the About page (System / 中文 / English).</item>
    </string-array>

